.SH NAME
Net::Nostr::RelayAccess \- NIP\-43 Relay Access Metadata and Requests
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 1
\&    use Net::Nostr::RelayAccess;
\&
\&    # Membership list (kind 13534)
\&    my $event = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->membership_list(
\&        pubkey  => $hex_pubkey,
\&        members => [$member_pk1, $member_pk2],
\&    );
\&
\&    # Add member (kind 8000)
\&    my $event = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->add_member(
\&        pubkey => $hex_pubkey,
\&        member => $member_pk,
\&    );
\&
\&    # Remove member (kind 8001)
\&    my $event = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->remove_member(
\&        pubkey => $hex_pubkey,
\&        member => $member_pk,
\&    );
\&
\&    # Join request (kind 28934)
\&    my $event = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->join_request(
\&        pubkey => $hex_pubkey,
\&        claim  => $invite_code,
\&    );
\&
\&    # Invite response (kind 28935)
\&    my $event = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->invite(
\&        pubkey => $hex_pubkey,
\&        claim  => $generated_code,
\&    );
\&
\&    # Leave request (kind 28936)
\&    my $event = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->leave_request(
\&        pubkey => $hex_pubkey,
\&    );
\&
\&    # Parse any relay access event
\&    my $parsed = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->from_event($event);
\&
\&    # Validate
\&    Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->validate($event);
.Ve
.SH DESCRIPTION
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
Implements NIP\-43 (Relay Access Metadata and Requests). Six event kinds
are used:
.IP \(bu 4
\&\fBMembership List\fR (kind 13534) \- A replaceable event
listing pubkeys that have access to a relay. MUST be signed by the
relay\*(Aqs NIP\-11 \f(CW\*(C`self\*(C'\fR pubkey. Contains \f(CW\*(C`member\*(C'\fR tags with hex
pubkeys.
.IP \(bu 4
\&\fBAdd Member\fR (kind 8000) \- Published when a member is added
to a relay. Contains a \f(CW\*(C`p\*(C'\fR tag with the member\*(Aqs hex pubkey.
.IP \(bu 4
\&\fBRemove Member\fR (kind 8001) \- Published when a member is
removed from a relay. Contains a \f(CW\*(C`p\*(C'\fR tag with the member\*(Aqs hex
pubkey.
.IP \(bu 4
\&\fBJoin Request\fR (kind 28934) \- An ephemeral event sent by a
user to request admission to a relay. MUST contain a \f(CW\*(C`claim\*(C'\fR tag
with an invite code.
.IP \(bu 4
\&\fBInvite\fR (kind 28935) \- An ephemeral event returned by a
relay with a claim string. Relays generate claims on the fly when
requested.
.IP \(bu 4
\&\fBLeave Request\fR (kind 28936) \- An ephemeral event sent by a
user to revoke their own access.
.PP
All six kinds MUST include a NIP\-70 \f(CW\*(C`["\-"]\*(C'\fR protected tag.
.SH CONSTRUCTOR
.IX Header "CONSTRUCTOR"
.SS new
.IX Subsection "new"
.Vb 3
\&    my $ra = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->new(
\&        members => [$member_pk],
\&    );
.Ve
.PP
Creates a new \f(CW\*(C`Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\*(C'\fR object. Croaks on unknown
arguments. \f(CW\*(C`members\*(C'\fR defaults to \f(CW\*(C`[]\*(C'\fR.
.SH "CLASS METHODS"
.IX Header "CLASS METHODS"
.SS membership_list
.IX Subsection "membership_list"
.Vb 4
\&    my $event = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->membership_list(
\&        pubkey  => $hex_pubkey,          # required
\&        members => [$member_pk, ...],    # optional, defaults to []
\&    );
.Ve
.PP
Creates a kind 13534 membership list Net::Nostr::Event. Automatically
includes the NIP\-70 \f(CW\*(C`["\-"]\*(C'\fR protected tag. Each member pubkey is
added as a \f(CW\*(C`["member", $pubkey]\*(C'\fR tag.
.SS add_member
.IX Subsection "add_member"
.Vb 4
\&    my $event = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->add_member(
\&        pubkey => $hex_pubkey,           # required
\&        member => $member_pk,            # required (p tag)
\&    );
.Ve
.PP
Creates a kind 8000 add\-member Net::Nostr::Event. Automatically
includes the NIP\-70 \f(CW\*(C`["\-"]\*(C'\fR protected tag.
.SS remove_member
.IX Subsection "remove_member"
.Vb 4
\&    my $event = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->remove_member(
\&        pubkey => $hex_pubkey,           # required
\&        member => $member_pk,            # required (p tag)
\&    );
.Ve
.PP
Creates a kind 8001 remove\-member Net::Nostr::Event. Automatically
includes the NIP\-70 \f(CW\*(C`["\-"]\*(C'\fR protected tag.
.SS join_request
.IX Subsection "join_request"
.Vb 4
\&    my $event = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->join_request(
\&        pubkey => $hex_pubkey,           # required
\&        claim  => $invite_code,          # required (claim tag)
\&    );
.Ve
.PP
Creates a kind 28934 join request Net::Nostr::Event. Automatically
includes the NIP\-70 \f(CW\*(C`["\-"]\*(C'\fR protected tag. The \f(CW\*(C`claim\*(C'\fR tag contains
the invite code.
.SS invite
.IX Subsection "invite"
.Vb 4
\&    my $event = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->invite(
\&        pubkey => $hex_pubkey,           # required
\&        claim  => $generated_code,       # required (claim tag)
\&    );
.Ve
.PP
Creates a kind 28935 invite Net::Nostr::Event. Automatically
includes the NIP\-70 \f(CW\*(C`["\-"]\*(C'\fR protected tag. The \f(CW\*(C`claim\*(C'\fR tag contains
the generated invite code.
.SS leave_request
.IX Subsection "leave_request"
.Vb 3
\&    my $event = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->leave_request(
\&        pubkey => $hex_pubkey,           # required
\&    );
.Ve
.PP
Creates a kind 28936 leave request Net::Nostr::Event. Automatically
includes the NIP\-70 \f(CW\*(C`["\-"]\*(C'\fR protected tag. No other tags are
required.
.SS from_event
.IX Subsection "from_event"
.Vb 1
\&    my $ra = Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->from_event($event);
.Ve
.PP
Parses a kind 13534, 8000, 8001, 28934, 28935, or 28936 event into a
\&\f(CW\*(C`Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\*(C'\fR object. Returns \f(CW\*(C`undef\*(C'\fR for unrecognized
kinds.
.SS validate
.IX Subsection "validate"
.Vb 1
\&    Net::Nostr::RelayAccess\->validate($event);
.Ve
.PP
Validates a NIP\-43 event. Croaks if:
.IP \(bu 4
Kind is not 13534, 8000, 8001, 28934, 28935, or 28936
.IP \(bu 4
Missing NIP\-70 \f(CW\*(C`["\-"]\*(C'\fR protected tag
.IP \(bu 4
Kind 8000/8001 missing \f(CW\*(C`p\*(C'\fR tag
.IP \(bu 4
Kind 28934/28935 missing \f(CW\*(C`claim\*(C'\fR tag
.PP
Returns 1 on success.
.SH ACCESSORS
.IX Header "ACCESSORS"
.SS members
.IX Subsection "members"
Arrayref of hex pubkeys from \f(CW\*(C`member\*(C'\fR tags (membership list only).
Defaults to \f(CW\*(C`[]\*(C'\fR.
.SS member
.IX Subsection "member"
Hex pubkey from \f(CW\*(C`p\*(C'\fR tag (add/remove member only).
.SS claim
.IX Subsection "claim"
Invite code string from \f(CW\*(C`claim\*(C'\fR tag (join request/invite only).
